00:01:48.600 --> 00:01:53.130
We believe that safety tools are critical digital infrastructure.

00:01:53.130 --> 00:01:57.080
We develop, distribute, maintain open source software for trust and

00:01:57.080 --> 00:01:57.770
safety.

00:01:57.770 --> 00:02:02.550
