We're not providing a hosted trust and safety platform.

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:13.480
We're not hosting this for you.

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:14.860
It's open, open source platform.

00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:17.790
You can host yourself and we're not doing your moderation for

00:02:17.790 --> 00:02:18.150
you.

