-profit and open source approach.

00:12:49.340 --> 00:12:54.540
The status quo that we found is really that trust and safety

00:12:54.540 --> 00:12:57.500
, like the larger industry, is kind of broken.

00:12:58.540 --> 00:13:04.000
As we've said, smaller platforms and newer protocols, a

00:13:04.020 --> 00:13:08.200
lot of indie small apps being built on AppProto especially

00:13:08.200 --> 00:13:10.960
, you might not know that you need these tools or they

