As a PDS hoster, your users, your liability

00:21:01.230 --> 00:21:01.500
.

00:21:01.500 --> 00:21:05.090
You might want to review reports against your community standards.

00:21:05.090 --> 00:21:06.060
You might want to, oh yeah.

