teams, but you also want to do right by your users

00:21:55.100 --> 00:21:55.340
.

00:21:55.340 --> 00:21:58.140
So you could use coop to set up some simple automation.

00:21:58.140 --> 00:21:59.860
If you want to do some manual review, you could do

00:21:59.870 --> 00:22:00.780
labeling of any kind.

